title: Belgium hold off profligate Mali (FIFA - Fédération Internationale de Football Association)
text: ( Source : FIFA - Fédération Internationale de Football Association ) Belgium and Mali played out an entertaining goalless draw in Talca , in which the African 's attacking prowess and flair was contained admirably by a sturdy Belgian defence.
